room_title: Escape room "Nashville" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: This will forever be my favorite escape room company!  As I have completed 25+ escape rooms across the country, the five I did with The Escape Game have been my favorite five.  Nashville was fun since I'm not from the area and it added to my tourist vibe of the town.  Would suggest for new and experienced escapees.

room_title: Escape room "Nashville" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: This was an absolute blast! Unique, clever, challenging, fun...a total rush! Will definitely be going back!

room_title: Escape room "Nashville" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: So, so much fun!! Can't wait to go back and try out the other rooms! #weescaped

room_title: Escape room "Nashville" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: Excellent way to spend a little money n time w friends! Super exciting and fast paced. With the clock ticking cooperation and paying attention is a must! Trust and questioning at the same time to figure out the clues!

room_title: Escape room "Nashville" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: Awesome! Our group ranged from 8 to 25. ( 8 year olds birthday ) All had a blast. We made it out The Heist with 7 seconds left! Ready to go to try all the rooms.

room_title: Escape room "Nashville" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: The 5 of us came out on Wednesday and played. We all had a great time! Jamie was an awesome host and gave us some great clues. We escaped (barely) and had such a fun time. We can't wait to come back again!

room_title: Escape room "Nashville" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: Just took my mom, friend, and sister for her 19th birthday. Beat the heist room with 2 and 1/2 minutes left! Great experience and the staff was amazing! Will be coming back to play another game!

room_title: Escape room "Nashville" by The Escape Game Nashville in Nashville
review: This was awesome!!! So much fun! Will definitely be back!! We did (parents) Nashville escape room and got out with 2 minutes to spare Kids did the same room with no as much luck! Lol
